### TransactionHistory entity HTTP tests
### TransactionHistory 전용 조회 API는 없어서 이벤트가 생성되는 흐름을 간접 검증합니다.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminEmail = hanaro
@adminPassword = 12345678
@userEmail = user1@test.com
@userPassword = 12345678
@transactionAccountNumber = 30100010004

### Admin 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### User 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("user_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### TransactionHistory SUBSCRIBE 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 8,
  "accountNumber": "{{transactionAccountNumber}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("tx_subscription_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### TransactionHistory TRANSFER 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriptionId": {{tx_subscription_id}},
  "amount": 25000,
  "fromAccountNumber": "12345678901"
}

### TransactionHistory TERMINATE 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/{{tx_subscription_id}}/terminate
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### TransactionHistory MATURED 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/maturity
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### TransactionHistory 간접 조회: 관리자 회원별 가입 상태 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/2/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

